gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Hawks 130, Wizards 121
gameRecap.excerpt: The Hawks defeated the Wizards, 130-121. Dejounte Murray recorded 24 points, four rebounds and 8 assists for the Hawks, while DeAndre Hunter (23 points, seven rebounds) and Trae Young (23 points, 10 assists) added a combined 46 points in the victory. Kyle Kuzma tallied a game-high 25 points, along with nine rebounds and six assists for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Hawks improve to 3-2 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 1-3.
